018d-0533-dd94-a9cd-47ff79b30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布周五在加沙战斗中丧生的以色列士兵姓名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/idf-releases-name-of-israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-combat-on-friday/0000018d-0469-dd07-a7df-cf7bcc5d0000</link><description>军士长。 (res.) 根据军方声明，24 岁的丹·瓦伊登鲍姆 (Dan Wajdenbaum) 被反坦克导弹炸死。此外，过去24小时内还有15名士兵受伤</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 20:24:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/idf-releases-name-of-israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-combat-on-friday/0000018d-0469-dd07-a7df-cf7bcc5d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列情报称哈马斯计划袭击海外目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/hamas-planned-attacks-on-targets-abroad-israeli-agencies-say/0000018d-0432-dd94-a9cd-46fe9dad0000</link><description>摩萨德和辛贝特表示，哈马斯在中东、非洲和欧洲策划恐怖袭击的阴谋被揭露后，三个欧洲国家被逮捕。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 20:02:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/hamas-planned-attacks-on-targets-abroad-israeli-agencies-say/0000018d-0432-dd94-a9cd-46fe9dad0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数千人抗议政府；抗议者封锁特拉维夫高速公路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-across-israel-against-the-government-dozens-block-tel-aviv-highway/0000018d-03f3-dd07-a7df-cbfbeb930000</link><description>警察强行驱散耶路撒冷的反战抗议者。 “要求更换政府及其领导人并不是政治声明。这是一个实事求是、事实和道德的声明，”约拉姆·布斯基拉中校在特拉维夫集会上说</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 19:19:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-across-israel-against-the-government-dozens-block-tel-aviv-highway/0000018d-03f3-dd07-a7df-cbfbeb930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列并未正式承认亚美尼亚种族灭绝，而是用它来嘲讽土耳其埃尔多安</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-doesnt-officially-recognize-the-armenian-genocide-but-uses-it-to-taunt-erdogan/0000018d-03cd-d832-a59d-17ff395e0000</link><description>据报道，作为以色列高级政治领导层对土耳其蓄意升级的一部分，以色列外交部长在推文中承认“土耳其犯下了亚美尼亚种族灭绝罪”</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 18:09:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-doesnt-officially-recognize-the-armenian-genocide-but-uses-it-to-taunt-erdogan/0000018d-03cd-d832-a59d-17ff395e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方下令向反内塔尼亚胡抗议组织者支付律师费</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-ordered-to-pay-legal-fees-of-anti-netanyahu-protest-organizer/0000018d-03a8-dd07-a7df-cbfa13020000</link><description>在抗议者告诉人群警方正在创造侵犯民主权利的条件后，法官猛烈抨击警方逮捕了抗议者并禁止他进入抗议现场</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 16:47:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-ordered-to-pay-legal-fees-of-anti-netanyahu-protest-organizer/0000018d-03a8-dd07-a7df-cbfa13020000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人在特拉维夫举行24小时大规模集会，要求释放加沙人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/24-hour-rally-for-release-of-hostages-held-in-gaza-set-to-take-place-in-tel-aviv/0000018d-0369-d832-a59d-17ffd4a10000</link><description>&amp;#39;世界在哪里？决策者在哪里？恳求人质的母亲 ■ 播放法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的视频致辞 ■ 计划周一上午在全国范围内进行 100 分钟的声援罢工</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 16:31:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/24-hour-rally-for-release-of-hostages-held-in-gaza-set-to-take-place-in-tel-aviv/0000018d-0369-d832-a59d-17ffd4a10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列妇女向正统男子提供非犹太三明治后，警方对她进行了询问</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/police-question-israeli-woman-after-she-offered-non-kosher-sandwich-to-orthodox-man/0000018d-022b-dd07-a7df-cb7b91010000</link><description>事件发生前一天，学校经理被记录与一名查巴德特使对峙，查巴德特使在学校正门前搭建了一个佩戴 Tefillin（命匣）的架子。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 10:25:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/police-question-israeli-woman-after-she-offered-non-kosher-sandwich-to-orthodox-man/0000018d-022b-dd07-a7df-cb7b91010000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高级警官被指控性行为不端</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/senior-israeli-police-officer-accused-of-sexual-misconduct/0000018d-0210-d832-a59d-16b78b180000</link><description>这名被指控违反信任罪的警官还被勒令离开车站一周。这名妇女正在嫌疑人监管的警察局中作为志愿者完成国民服役</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 09:23:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/senior-israeli-police-officer-accused-of-sexual-misconduct/0000018d-0210-d832-a59d-16b78b180000</guid></item><item><title>“南非声称哈马斯并不存在，一切都是以色列造成的”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/two-days-of-genocide-hearings-at-the-hague-conclude-as-israel-enters-worlds-microscope/0000018c-ffef-d517-af9d-ffff79140000</link><description>国际法学者虽然赞扬以色列团队在联合国最高法院的辩护，但他们预测以色列团队将出台临时措施，可能损害以色列形象，造成政治、外交和法律伤害</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 07:42:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/two-days-of-genocide-hearings-at-the-hague-conclude-as-israel-enters-worlds-microscope/0000018c-ffef-d517-af9d-ffff79140000</guid></item><item><title>“我有土地，但我没有”：西岸橄榄收成是加沙战争的又一受害者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-01-13/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/i-have-land-but-i-dont-west-bank-olive-harvest-is-yet-another-casualty-of-gaza-war/0000018c-ff8e-dd94-a9cc-ffeeb6910000</link><description>加沙战争使约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦人的生活变得困难。除了检查站和封闭的道路外，橄榄园也被宣布为禁区。上周收割结束后，三分之一的农作物仍留在树上，剥夺了巴勒斯坦人生计的一个关键要素</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 05:12:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-01-13/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/i-have-land-but-i-dont-west-bank-olive-harvest-is-yet-another-casualty-of-gaza-war/0000018c-ff8e-dd94-a9cc-ffeeb6910000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军：四名试图从黎巴嫩渗透以色列的恐怖分子被军队击毙；卡塔尔收到向加沙以色列人质提供的药品</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article-live/u-s-continues-strikes-against-houthis-in-yemen-rockets-fired-at-gaza-border-communities/0000018d-007e-dd07-a7df-cb7e2a050000</link><description>以色列国防军：以色列军队击毙了四名试图从黎巴嫩渗透以色列领土的恐怖分子 ■ 根据卡塔尔斡旋的协议，药品将在“未来几天内”转移给加沙的以色列人质，该协议也将导致更多药品进入加沙 ■ 报告：以色列之间的争端和埃及就以色列意图控制埃及-加沙边境地区 ■ 美国袭击萨那的胡塞武装目标</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 03:07:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article-live/u-s-continues-strikes-against-houthis-in-yemen-rockets-fired-at-gaza-border-communities/0000018d-007e-dd07-a7df-cb7e2a050000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在约旦河西岸定居点附近发生枪击事件，以色列国防军击毙三名恐怖分子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-wounded-in-shooting-near-west-bank-settlement-idf-kills-three-terrorists/0000018c-ffb1-d832-a59d-ffb7c3ee0000</link><description>周五晚上，三名枪手渗透到约旦河西岸的阿多拉定居点，通过外围围栏的缺口进入，并在与以色列国防军的交火中丧生。建议居民将自己锁在家里直到早上</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 22:22:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-wounded-in-shooting-near-west-bank-settlement-idf-kills-three-terrorists/0000018c-ffb1-d832-a59d-ffb7c3ee0000</guid></item><item><title>南非犹太板球运动员在世界杯前被解除 U-19 国家队队长职务</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/jewish-south-african-cricketer-removed-as-captain-of-u-19-natl-team-ahead-of-world-cup/0000018c-fe33-d832-a59d-feb773b60000</link><description>大卫·蒂格因公开支持在加沙作战的以色列士兵而被正式免职，原因是即将举行的 19 岁以下板球世界杯存在安全问题</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 19:41:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/jewish-south-african-cricketer-removed-as-captain-of-u-19-natl-team-ahead-of-world-cup/0000018c-fe33-d832-a59d-feb773b60000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡表示，药品将在“未来几天内”转移给加沙的以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-medicine-will-be-transferred-to-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-in-the-next-few-days/0000018c-fed6-d517-af9d-fefebbf10000</link><description>卡塔尔斡旋的协议将允许向以色列人质提供处方药，而以色列将允许更多药品进入加沙</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 18:32:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-medicine-will-be-transferred-to-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-in-the-next-few-days/0000018c-fed6-d517-af9d-fefebbf10000</guid></item></channel></rss>